@startuml diagrama-construtor-grafos

title Bloco 3 — JSON → quatro grafos (mapeamento de logins)

left to right direction

package contrato {
  class InteractionRow <<DTO>> {
    + source_user : str
    + target_user : str
    + type : str
    + weight : float
    + ...
  }
}

package construtor {
  class UserMapper {
    + id_for(login) : int
    + login_for(id) : str
    + size() : int
    + ...
  }

  class GraphBuilder {
    + build(rows: list[InteractionRow]) : GraphBundle
    + ...
  }

  class GraphBundle {
    + comments : AbstractGraph
    + issue_closes : AbstractGraph
    + pr_events : AbstractGraph
    + integrated : AbstractGraph
    + mapper : UserMapper
    + ...
  }
}

package grafo {
  abstract class AbstractGraph
  class AdjacencyMatrixGraph
  class AdjacencyListGraph
}

GraphBuilder ..> InteractionRow
GraphBuilder --> UserMapper
GraphBuilder ..> AbstractGraph : cria (matriz|lista)
GraphBundle o-- UserMapper
GraphBundle o-- AbstractGraph : x4 instâncias
AbstractGraph <|-- AdjacencyMatrixGraph
AbstractGraph <|-- AdjacencyListGraph

note bottom of GraphBuilder
  Filtra por ``type`` para G1/G2/G3; **G4** agrega pesos no par (u→v).
end note

@enduml
